

# 安防管理优化

## APP端

1.1 巡查预警类型传入的应该是预警类型编号， 而不是 名称

![image-20231012151912764](https://gitee.com/chen-jiujia/typora-picgo/raw/master/img/202310121519891.png)

## 首页

1.1 点击巡查点之后应添加原型图所框内容。

![image-20231012142113235](https://gitee.com/chen-jiujia/typora-picgo/raw/master/img/202310121421400.png)

1.2 首页这两个预警图标点击之后，显示的内容应和【视频监控】模块中的一致

![](https://gitee.com/chen-jiujia/typora-picgo/raw/master/img/202310121434616.png)

![image-20231012142600956](https://gitee.com/chen-jiujia/typora-picgo/raw/master/img/202310121426106.png)

![image-20231012143615403](https://gitee.com/chen-jiujia/typora-picgo/raw/master/img/202310121436613.png)

